{"tid":1261190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"86歲老翁於特首辦外噴上「鄭月娥包庇凶犯、葵涌醫院傷天害理」   被律政司指「有被害妄想症」","createTime":"2019-06-27T06:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:18:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57499121ba8fd607bff1eafeb14552b508463df8","tid":1261190,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1465323_1_L_20190627133306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1465323_1_L_20190627133306.jpg&h=9e30f0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465323-20190627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465323-20190627.htm&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=5377d884\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465323-20190627.htm&h=2a04a681\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465323-20190627.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n一名86歲老翁涉嫌在特首辦外，用白色噴漆在牆壁上噴上字句，被控一項刑事毀壞罪，今日在東區法院提堂，裁判官將案押後至8月22日以索取被告的精神報告，被告繼續獲准保釋。 <br />\n<br />\n被告黃林被控於去年11月19日，在金鐘添華道特首辦外，出入口牆壁上以簡體字噴寫「鄭月娥包庇凶犯、葵涌醫院傷天害理」，控方表示，被告患有被害妄想症，會先取兩份精神科報告，以考慮被告是否適合答辯。"},{"pid":"b60fd76c6e092ff785b54fdb4c2031c70a18a0ee","tid":1261190,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"支那政治犯，全部有精神席"}]}